underlying_goal: To correct an error in a previous edit where content was deleted instead of being marked as deprecated.
friction_detail: Claude had previously deleted content that should have been struck through, requiring the user to point out the error and have it corrected.
primary_success: Quickly understanding the error and correctly restoring the deleted content while applying the intended strikethrough formatting.
brief_summary: The user pointed out that Claude had mistakenly deleted content from a spec file instead of striking it through. Claude acknowledged the error, restored the missing information, and correctly applied the strikethrough formatting to deprecated options.
